<?php $__env->startSection('postContent'); ?><h2>GENERAL INFORMATION</h2>
<p>All students are expected to wear the prescribed school uniform in a tidy manner. Parents are asked to support the school in achieving this expectation.</p>
<p>The Board of Trustees has delegated to the Principal the authority to rule on all matters relating to uniform, jewellery, hair and standards of personal presentation.</p>
<p>Summer uniform is worn in Terms One and Four. Winter uniform is worn in Terms Two and Three.</p>
<p>Cycle helmets are compulsory as required by law.</p>
